Package: Sonnet
Title: Modern Network Visualization for R
Version: 1.5.1
Authors@R:
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", , "mohammed.saqr@uef.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modern, extensible network visualization package that provides
    high-quality static and interactive network plots. Sonnet accepts adjacency
    matrices, edge lists, or igraph objects and offers customizable layouts,
    node shapes, edge styles, and themes. Designed for publication-ready
    visualizations with a pipe-friendly API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/lamethods/Sonnet
BugReports: https://github.com/lamethods/Sonnet/issues
